*NIX Installation:
    git clone git://github.com/bobbychopra/dotvimfiles.git ~/.vim
    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

  Create symlinks:
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc


WINDOWS Installation
    cd C:\Program Files\Vim
    git clone git://github.com/bobbychopra/dotvimfiles.git vimfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

  Create hardlinks (for windows):
    C:\Program Files\Vim>fsutil hardlink create _vimrc vimfiles\vimrc
